localString.value: Made from a fine silk, this robe seems to have a permanent aura of light around it.

The grease covered contraption before you contains the necessary tools, clamps, cutter, vials and other assorted bits needed to use the tinkering skill. A tinkerer tool is needed to activate and use parts of the set.
Hearty billows fan the forge-borne flames. The air is blisteringly hot, leaving you feel light-headed and not quite yourself.

This sturdy blacksmith's anvil bears the dented sheen of long use. Something in you wonders what great weapons and armor have been shaped upon its well-worn surface.

This is a jeweler's desk used for making jewelry.
This desk is used by tailors to make belts, cloaks, clothes, gloves, leather armors, bags, boots, dyes, cloths and cloth padding.
The weapons lean into the wooden rack, waiting for release.
This is a fletchers desk used for making arrows.
